Package cmput301w16t08.scaling_pancake.models

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Bid
    Bid is meant to represent a bid made by a User (called the bidder) on an Instrument.
    BidList
    BidList is meant to hold a list of Bid objects.
    Instrument
    Instrument is meant represent an instrument owned by a specific User (called the owner), and contains a list of Bids on the instrument
    InstrumentList
    InstrumentList is meant to hold a list of Instrument objects.
    User
    User is meant to represent a user, and contains lists of Instruments he owns and has borrowed, as well as pending Bids.
    UserList
    UserList is meant to hold a list of User objects.
